# Register of domain numbers for PMDAs in PCP.
#
# PMDA Name should be in UPPERCASE to support automated
# changes in PMDA build and install procedures for PMDA code,
# PMNS fragments, help text, etc.  It must also be a valid
# C (or cpp more strictly) identifier and unique across all
# PMDAs.
#
# PMDA Name	Domain Number
#
